01:17:39.521 --> 01:17:40.579
O.K.

01:17:40.656 --> 01:17:46.788
Um...Steve is making
significant improvement.

01:17:46.862 --> 01:17:47.988
He is?

01:17:48.063 --> 01:17:49.758
Significant improvement.

01:17:49.831 --> 01:17:51.765
If I were in your shoes,

01:17:51.833 --> 01:17:53.460
