01:19:07.776 --> 01:19:09.243
My first World Series,

01:19:09.311 --> 01:19:12.280
at least in the capacity
of play-by-play man,

01:19:12.347 --> 01:19:13.780
For you, Tim, your eighth,

01:19:13.849 --> 01:19:15.783
Relax, It's a piece of cake,

