01:21:26.581 --> 01:21:28.014
I got to go pitch

01:21:28.083 --> 01:21:30.415
the first game
of the World Series now.

01:21:30.485 --> 01:21:32.146
So I'm going to go.

01:21:32.220 --> 01:21:35.678
If Nebraska pitches the perfect game
many are predicting,

01:21:35.757 --> 01:21:37.622
